node.text:
EPIC video from Finns Beach Club! They’ve partnered with Bali Tourism Board, Wonderful Indonesia and Garuda Airlines with an incredible offer to get the world #backtobali ! 
When you buy a Back To Bali voucher, your initial payment TRIPLES in value to spend on food and drinks, accommodation and Finns Bali memberships during your next holiday to Bali, plus exclusive access to discounts on accommodation, adventures, dining experiences and more! 
Here’s the link for vouchers - these are 100% going to sell out so get in quick. https://finns.to/SagQ3
I’ve got mine - I’ll see you in Bali! 
Follow @finnsbeachclub for more info.

node.text:
Pressure 
The strongest souls of this world are those that have both felt immense pressure, and overcome it 
This Lion King didn’t get here by cowering away from opposition; even when it’s 20 to 1 
And even with help, that is why he is the King 
Video by © BBC Earth @bbcearth

node.text:
The Eternal Couple
.
Saaya and Cleopatra have been courting since 4 years now and whenever they are together it’s a sight to behold. The forest comes alive as they trot nonchalantly in his fabled kingdom. Usually in the courting pairs generally it is the Male who takes charge and moves around with the female following close behind. But with this couple it was definitely Cleo who was in charge while the Panther followed. 

Photos by @mithunhphotography

Precious moments with the @moonfamilylife during their travels. ☺️ From New Zealand and Mexico to states like Wyoming and Colorado, the Moon Family inspires many with their incredible family adventures outdoors. 🏕

Spending time in nature allows you to be present and focus on what matters the most. Not only is it a great way to spend quality time with your loved ones, but also improves your mood and boosts overall well-being. 🍃

What kind of places do you usually travel to with your family? 😍

📸 @moonfamilylife

node.text:
DOMINICAN TREE HOUSE STAY GIVEAWAY!! 🌴🇩🇴

We are giving you and a friend a chance to win an epic trip to the Dominican Republic!

The winner will receive 5 days/4 nights and 2x $500 airplane ticket credit to stay at the beautiful eco-resort @dominicantreehousevillage. All meals, bottomless local rum drinks, juices, sodas, water included! This trip also includes 2 zipline excursions, bicycle rentals, and nightly onsite activities.

Explore the lush jungle of the Samana province in the Dominican Republic, a natural resort of open-air cabins perched above the forest floor!

To Enter:
1) Follow @dominicantreehousevillage, @wonderlustcollective, @fastnewsfacts
2) Tag friends in separate comments
3) Visit the link in @wonderlustcollective bio and enter your email
1 Comment = 1 Entry. Unlimited Entries
**BONUS** Share this Post in your Story and Tag Us

A winner will be chosen on 9/3 and announced via @wonderlustcollective.

Winner has until the end of August 2022 to reserve. Not redeemable for cash value.
*
Subject to availability blackout dates.
*
Travel to and from location is not provided
-
We will never DM you any links to claim prize!
-
Good luck!! ❤️
-
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)
